Have just bought all games by this creator as my kids have enjoyed the first few so much. Unlike other educational games these seem polished with enough variety to keep little ones engrossed. Recommended!

We have this and Bugs and Buttons for android. My kids who are 4, 6, and 8 all love it. They play them regularly. Lots of fun learning activities in each game. I also have Bug Art and Bug Mazing on ipad along with some others that are ipad only at the moment. They had a big package deal of them there. Highly recommend.
